================================================================================

Our Original Contributions
================================================================================

The following components are original work created for this project:

Smart Contracts & Deployment:
- blockchain_contracts/contracts/CitizenSBT.sol (Soulbound Token for identity verification)
- blockchain_contracts/contracts/VotingWithSBT.sol (Vote contract with SBT validation)
- blockchain_contracts/contracts/VotingRewardNFT.sol (ERC-721 reward NFT)
- blockchain_contracts/contracts/NFTEscrow.sol (NFT trading escrow contract)
- blockchain_contracts/deploy_sbt_system.js (SBT system deployment script)
- blockchain_contracts/scripts/setup_and_deploy.sh (Automated deployment)
- blockchain_contracts/scripts/redeploy_contract.sh (Re-deployment utility)

Backend API (Phase 2 - Email Verification):
- api/request-code.js (OTP email request)
- api/verify-and-sign.js (Code verification and signature generation)
- api/check-status.js (Verification status check)
- api/complete-verification.js (Transaction completion notification)
- api/_lib/crypto.js (Cryptographic utilities)
- api/_lib/email.js (Email sending via Resend)
- api/_lib/supabase.js (Supabase integration)
- api/_lib/rate-limit.js (API rate limiting)

NFT Trading System (Phase 3):
- api/nft-trading/deposits.js (NFT deposit management)
- api/nft-trading/swap.js (NFT swap execution)
- api/nft-trading/withdraw.js (NFT withdrawal)
- api/nft-trading/_lib.js (Shared trading utilities)
- scripts/escrow_indexer.js (Blockchain event indexing)

Frontend UI (React + TypeScript):
- frontend/src/pages/EmailVerificationPage.tsx (Email verification flow)
- frontend/src/pages/VotingApp.tsx (Voting interface)
- frontend/src/pages/MyNFTsPage.tsx (NFT collection display)
- frontend/src/pages/NFTExchangePage.tsx (NFT trading marketplace)
- frontend/src/lib/emailVerificationApi.ts (Email API client)
- frontend/src/lib/nftEscrowApi.ts (NFT trading API client)
- frontend/src/stores/emailVerificationStore.ts (Auth state management)
- frontend/src/stores/nftTradingStore.ts (Trading state management)

Database Schema (Supabase):
- supabase/migrations/ (Database schema definitions)

Documentation & Configuration:
- README.md (Comprehensive project documentation)
- docs/ARCHITECTURE.md (System architecture guide)
- docs/nft-trading-system-spec.md (NFT trading specification)
- frontend/RUN_GUIDE.md (Frontend execution guide)
- .github/copilot-instructions.md (AI agent development guide)
- blockchain_contracts/deploy.env.example (Deployment configuration template)

