================================================================================
Project Summary
================================================================================

This is a complete blockchain voting system with:
- SBT-based identity verification (CitizenSBT)
- Secure email OTP authentication
- Smart contract-based voting (VotingWithSBT)
- Participation reward NFTs (VotingRewardNFT)
- NFT trading with escrow mechanism (NFTEscrow)
- Integrated React web interface
- Automated deployment and indexing

Version: 3.0.0
Last Updated: 2025-12-05
